body:
Summaries are shown again, but the navigation is still broken. In the log there is still this error:

```
WARNING:tensorflow:IOError [Errno 2] No such file or directory: '/usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/external/paper-tabs/paper-tabs.html' on path /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/external/paper-tabs/paper-tabs.html
```

And clicking on e. g. `images` does redirect to `http://localhost:6006/#null`. Manually entering `http://localhost:6006/#images` works.
